ke":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f85ffb31590b3c47a6646d5515dd4e4fc642356a","tid":1283963,"uid":522,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:41:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">團結、持之以恆、不怕死的信念</span></strong></span><br />\n烏克蘭的結果大家都知。其實看擺整個電影，你不會有一個示威者完全取勝的感覺，因為它是一個現實的紀錄片，不是看動作片打遊戲機，不會有個最後大佬給你打。示威者沒有佔領到總統府，而且由頭到尾一直也是「挨打」的狀態，他們沒有槍械，只有自製燃料彈、石頭及盾牌，打起上來永遠是傷亡慘重，但他們明知不夠打，也要打下去。民眾能推翻政權的原因，除了一點政治因素之外，也是因為連本身腐敗的議會也抵受不住壓力，不再支持總統亞努科維奇。這也全靠民眾的團結、持之以恆，以及一個寧為玉碎、不作瓦全的心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/2016-02-12-16_19_07-768x428.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F02%2F2016-02-12-16_19_07-768x428.png&h=bfef8e37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲看著同伴被抓、重傷、殺死，示威者示死如歸，再沒有顧慮。這個狀態旁人很難理解到。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/2016-02-12-16_45_27-768x428.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F02%2F2016-02-12-16_45_27-768x428.png&h=a090de88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲「他們立志改善國家現況，所以他們願意走在子彈下」情操高尚。不過在香港，可能被視為暴徒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/2016-02-12-16_33_58-768x428.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F02%2F2016-02-12-16_33_58-768x428.png&h=72706879&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/2016-02-12-16_32_28-768x428.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F02%2F2016-02-12-16_32_28-768x428.png&h=8500946a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/2016-02-12-14_05_33-768x428.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F02%2F2016-02-12-14_05_33-768x428.png&h=93ba7b95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原文 : <a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2016/02/14/netflix_winter_on_fire/column/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2016%2F02%2F14%2Fnetflix_winter_on_fire%2Fcolumn%2F&d=U4JEvS4lHdpitRbH3ga0O%2BQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=fa534f00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2016/02/14/netflix_winter_on_fire/column/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T12:34:59.000Z","msg":"係寫就寫埋烏克蘭個結果黎<br />\n篇野咁講就完咗 好多人會以為結果係比人暴力鎮壓完就完咗 會驚 會唔再支持<br />\n咁就會錯意<br />\n<br />\n記住 當你以為係最撚黑暗既時候 堅持埋佢 黎明就會喺下一秒來臨"},{"pid":"4a49682154f1ddcbabc836f1406f36925b0118cd","tid":1283963,"uid":82394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:38:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fc62ed41d2a386b3ff67a38f05ef39939b18340","tid":1283963,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:01:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58d2daaf9031c37d89e05bb78a554867dcab28ed","tid":1283963,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:15:20.000Z","msg":"要推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"765c9a7085be8da99cbd4a78fe10e934678a9d90","tid":1283963,"uid":31132,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:18:31.000Z","msg":"好好睇，後面十六歲打比阿媽講遺言個幕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8225211b26a